						               													<description>Atlas in a Box is a spin-off from &amp;quot;Take Off&amp;quot; and consists of the full deck of cards from &amp;quot;Take Off,&amp;quot; a small, color paper map of the world, and new instructions of games to play with the cards.  The games include flag- and map-matching, ranking countries and taking tricks, as well as a straight quiz game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Can you name this country?  If not, don't worry because Atlas-in-a-Box is a delightful card game that can teach you world geography with fascinating facts and lots of fun.  Here's what you get:&amp;#10;Detailed country cards -- nearly 200 in all! -- from the award -winning board game Take Off!  The cards profiles the nations of the world with flags, maps, and much more.&amp;#10;A full-color political map.  The map shows the whole world at a glance, and include a complete country index.&amp;#10;Four easy-to-play games.  The games turn the cards and world map into adventures in fun while unlocking a wealth of knowledge.&amp;#10;Whether for the home, the classroom, or on the go, this portable Atlas-in-a-Box is the ideal year-round gift for families and students -- or even yourself.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
